  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">In this letter, William Lloyd Garrison introduces his abolitionist friend Joshua Coffin. The Liberator is causing &quot;extraordinary movements&quot; among whites in the slave states. Garrison writes: &quot;I am constantly receiving anonymous letters, filled with abominable and bloody sentiments. These trouble me less than the wind. I never was so happy and confident in my mind as at the present time.&quot;</subfield>
